description: On episode 13 of Pranksters, muscular Blaze Austin is giving his unsuspecting victims serious wedgies! Everything is going his way until he ends up on chiseled hunk Jake Porter, who happens to be wearing lacy, pink panties! Brown-haired Blaze jumps back, but he’s actually turned on, and follows Jake back home so he can get up close and personal.
title: Pranksters Part 13
